{"id": "vhw1665702560221", "title": "setocc", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Statements", "setocc"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vhw1665702560221.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">setocc</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: setformfocus \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: setformfocus \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tod1665702665614.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: show \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: show \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qgc1665702595858.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/vhw1665702560221.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/vhw1665702560221.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/vhw1665702560221.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533028\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533028\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vhw1665702560221.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vhw1665702560221.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vhw1665702560221.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vhw1665702560221\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__setocc_239288\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Make a specific occurrence the current occurrence.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__topic_d77168e1_d77169e1_d77170e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__p_d77171e1_d77172e1_d77173e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">,</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceNumber</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__section_w2197ab1b7b5_w2198ab1b7_w2199ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__p_d77174e1_d77175e1_d77176e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">setocc CUSTOMER, 1</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__topic_d50732e1_d50733e1_d50734e1_d50735e1_d50736e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d151635e82\">Parameters </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7394e1_d7395e1_d7396e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7394e1_d7395e1_d7396e1__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7394e1_d7395e1_d7396e1__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7394e1_d7395e1_d7396e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7394e1_d7395e1_d7396e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7394e1_d7395e1_d7396e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7394e1_d7395e1_d7396e1__entry__3\">\n Entity in which an occurrence is to be made current. Can be \"*\", in which case all entities in the current instance are set to the occurrence specified.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7394e1_d7395e1_d7396e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7394e1_d7395e1_d7396e1__entry__2\">\n Number\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7394e1_d7395e1_d7396e1__entry__3\">\n Sequence number of the occurrence in the component; whole (integer) number; the value will be truncated to form an integer.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__topic_d50737e1_d50738e1_d50739e1_d50740e1_d50741e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d151635e151\">Return Values </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7397e1_d7398e1_d7399e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values Returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7397e1_d7398e1_d7399e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7397e1_d7398e1_d7399e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7397e1_d7398e1_d7399e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7397e1_d7398e1_d7399e1__entry__2\">\n An error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7397e1_d7398e1_d7399e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&gt;=0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7397e1_d7398e1_d7399e1__entry__2\">\n Sequence number of the new current occurrence in <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7400e1_d7401e1_d7402e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values Commonly Returned by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7400e1_d7401e1_d7402e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7400e1_d7401e1_d7402e1__entry__2\">\n Error constant\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7400e1_d7401e1_d7402e1__entry__3\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7400e1_d7401e1_d7402e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7400e1_d7401e1_d7402e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UGENERR_ERROR&gt;</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7400e1_d7401e1_d7402e1__entry__3\">\n An error occurred. <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> is the outer entity of a Record component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7400e1_d7401e1_d7402e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7400e1_d7401e1_d7402e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7400e1_d7401e1_d7402e1__entry__3\">\n The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7400e1_d7401e1_d7402e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">-1203</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7400e1_d7401e1_d7402e1__entry__2\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_RANGE&gt;</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"vhw1665702560221__table_d7400e1_d7401e1_d7402e1__entry__3\"> Value out of range. For example,\n                           <var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceNumber</var> is greater than the number of\n                        occurrences of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__topic_d50742e1_d50743e1_d50744e1_d50745e1_d50746e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d151635e316\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__topic_d50747e1_d50748e1_d50749e1_d50750e1_d50751e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d151635e325\">Description </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__p_d77192e1_d77193e1_d77194e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span> statement makes current\n            the occurrence of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> that is identified by\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceNumber</var>. If <var class=\"keyword varname\">OccurrenceNumber</var> is:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__li_d32966e1_d32967e1_d32968e1\">&lt;0—last occurrence in the hitlist becomes current. This entails fetching all the occurrences in the hitlist.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__li_d32969e1_d32970e1_d32971e1\">0 or not specified—current occurrence is not changed.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__li_d32972e1_d32973e1_d32974e1\">Between 1 and the current number of occurrences of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> in the component, inclusive—indicated occurrence becomes current.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__li_d32975e1_d32976e1_d32977e1\">Greater than the number of occurrences of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> in the component—<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set to -1 and the current occurrence remains current.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__p_d77195e1_d77196e1_d77197e1\">Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span> to change the current occurrence causes the getFocus trigger to be activated when the trigger containing the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span> completes. The getFocus trigger is only activated once, though, for the occurrence that is active at the end of the trigger containing the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span> statement.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__p_d77198e1_d77199e1_d77200e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span> has an immediate effect on the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span>. For example, a statement such as <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$entname</span>,<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc+1</span> immediately increments the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$curocc</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__p_d77201e1_d77202e1_d77203e1\">The statement <code class=\"ph codeph\">setocc \"*\",-1</code> does not return a total number of occurrences in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>, because the painted entities are not likely to have the same number of occurrences.</p>\n<div class=\"note caution note_caution\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__note_w2200ab1b7c13c13_w2201ab1b7c13_w2202ab1b7_w2203ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">CAUTION:</span> Be careful with statements such as <code class=\"ph codeph\">setocc \"*\",-1</code>,\n            since they can have drastic effects when combined with statements like\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">erase</span>. Issuing an <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">erase</span> after a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc\n               \"*\",-1</span> removes all the data that matches the profile given by the user in\n            the entities of the component.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__section_hp5_cdm_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d151635e429\">Example: Giving Focus to the Last Occurrence in a Component </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span> to find the last\n            customer number used in the database:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__pre_qzg_ddm_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation exec\n; fetch all occurrences into component\n\nretrieve\nsetocc \"CUSTOMER\",-1\nmessage \"Last customer is %%custnumber%%%.\"\nedit\nend; exec</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__section_mpw_1dm_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d151635e444\">Example: Looping Through a Hitlist and Checking Occurrences</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example shows the use of the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">setocc</span>\n            statement to loop through a hitlist, checking that all occurrences have been entered by\n            the user.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"vhw1665702560221__pre_mg3_bdm_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger accept\n\n$occ_num$ = 1\nrepeat\n setocc \"ENTRANT\", $occ_num$\n if (DRIVER_ID.ENTRANT = 0)\n message/info/nobeep \"Not all places have been filled. %/\n Please complete the grid or Cancel.\"\n return(-1)\n endif\n $occ_num$ = $occ_num$ + 1\nuntil ($occ_num$ &gt; $totocc(ENTRANT))\nend; accept</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yrm1665702560304.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>creocc</a><p>Creates an empty occurrence of the specified entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fpg1665702560533.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>remocc</a><p>Mark an occurrence of the specified entity for deletion at the next store.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cyd1665702599286.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>retrieve</a><p>Activate the read trigger for the first outermost entity and all related entities, or for a specific entity.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exa1665702598712.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$curocc</a><p>Return the sequence number of the current occurrence in the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jnc1665702576977.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$entname</a><p>Return the name of the current entity or check for the existence of an entity in the component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rmp1665702598941.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$totocc</a><p>Return the number of occurrences of an entity in the component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533028\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533028\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "setocc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Make a specific occurrence the current occurrence. setocc Entity , OccurrenceNumber Example: setocc CUSTOMER, 1 Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity in which an occurrence is to be made current. Can be \"*\", in which case all entities in the current instance are set to the occurrence specified. OccurrenceNumber Number Sequence number of the occurrence in the component; whole (integer) number; the value will be truncated to form an integer. Return Values Table 2. Values Returned in $status Value Meaning <0 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. >=0 Sequence number of the new current occurrence in Entity . Table 3. Values Commonly Returned by $procerror following setocc Value Error constant Meaning -1 <UGENERR_ERROR> An error occurred. Entity is the outer entity of a Record component. -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. -1203 <UPROCERR_RANGE> Value out of range. For example, OccurrenceNumber is greater than the number of occurrences of Entity . Use Allowed in all component types. Description The setocc statement makes current the occurrence of Entity that is identified by OccurrenceNumber . If OccurrenceNumber is: <0—last occurrence in the hitlist becomes current. This entails fetching all the occurrences in the hitlist. 0 or not specified—current occurrence is not changed. Between 1 and the current number of occurrences of Entity in the component, inclusive—indicated occurrence becomes current. Greater than the number of occurrences of Entity in the component— $status is set to -1 and the current occurrence remains current. Using setocc to change the current occurrence causes the getFocus trigger to be activated when the trigger containing the setocc completes. The getFocus trigger is only activated once, though, for the occurrence that is active at the end of the trigger containing the setocc statement. setocc has an immediate effect on the value of $curocc . For example, a statement such as setocc $entname , $curocc+1 immediately increments the value of $curocc . The statement setocc \"*\",-1 does not return a total number of occurrences in $status , because the painted entities are not likely to have the same number of occurrences. CAUTION: Be careful with statements such as setocc \"*\",-1 , since they can have drastic effects when combined with statements like erase . Issuing an erase after a setocc \"*\",-1 removes all the data that matches the profile given by the user in the entities of the component. Example: Giving Focus to the Last Occurrence in a Component The following example uses setocc to find the last customer number used in the database: operation exec ; fetch all occurrences into component retrieve setocc \"CUSTOMER\",-1 message \"Last customer is %%custnumber%%%.\" edit end; exec Copy Example: Looping Through a Hitlist and Checking Occurrences The following example shows the use of the setocc statement to loop through a hitlist, checking that all occurrences have been entered by the user. trigger accept $occ_num$ = 1 repeat setocc \"ENTRANT\", $occ_num$ if (DRIVER_ID.ENTRANT = 0) message/info/nobeep \"Not all places have been filled. %/ Please complete the grid or Cancel.\" return(-1) endif $occ_num$ = $occ_num$ + 1 until ($occ_num$ > $totocc(ENTRANT)) end; accept Copy Related Links creocc Creates an empty occurrence of the specified entity. remocc Mark an occurrence of the specified entity for deletion at the next store. retrieve Activate the read trigger for the first outermost entity and all related entities, or for a specific entity. $curocc Return the sequence number of the current occurrence in the hitlist. $entname Return the name of the current entity or check for the existence of an entity in the component. $totocc Return the number of occurrences of an entity in the component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}